J C Watts Jr BiographyJ.C. Watts, Jr., is a dynamic preacher, congressman, and father of six. Currently serving his fourth and final congressional term, he is the Republican Conference chairman.J. C. Watts  was born in 1957. 
Biography
J.C. Watts, Jr., is a dynamic preacher, congressman, and father of six. Currently serving his fourth and final congressional term, he is the Republican Conference chairman.J. C. Watts  was born in 1957. 
